  "parent": "sla",
  "notes": "Standard Belarusian (Tarashkevitsa/Narkamaŭka). Distinctive features: ⟨г⟩ = [ɣ] (voiced velar fricative, not plosive), ⟨ў⟩ = [w] (unique letter for non-syllabic /w/), pervasive аканне (unstressed /ɔ/ → [a]), яканне (unstressed /ɛ/ → [i] after soft consonants), full affricate writing: ⟨дз⟩ = [dz], ⟨дж⟩ = [dʒ].",
